item.title: 【HD Live Performances】WEB-RiP - Taylor Swift - The Eras Tour, SoFi Stadium, 2023 [4K, fixed song order, bonus audio bootleg]
item.description:
The Eras Tour is a fantastic show and possibly the best of all time so far. It's a must have for any pop fan. This is the 4K version (HEVC video) and I included an audio bootleg made by me as a bonus!

Video originally ripped by FLUX, then edited by me (Caladan): I moved the bonus songs The Archer, Long Live and Wildest Dreams to their right place in setlist from the end of the show, I added a stereo audio track converted from the original Dolby Digital Plus 5.1 audio track, I added precise chapters for each song, I fixed some technical issues of the English subtitles, I added a cover image, I added this info file.

The quality is identical to the FLUX release (NO re-encoding). Warning: this is a big video (27GB). You can get the Full HD version from here.

Programs used for editing this video recording:
- lossless video editing: MKVToolNix, Avidemux;
- muxing: MKVToolNix;
- demuxing: gMKVExtractGUI;
- chapters editing: MKVToolNix;
- subtitles fixing: Subtitle Edit;
- making the stereo track from the original 5.1 audio track: FFmpeg and Audacity.
